params.agentId: The ID of the agent to pause

params.ensName: The ENS name to look up

returns._0: agentId The agent ID if found, 0 if not found

returns._0: Array of agent IDs owned by the address

returns._0: True if agent is active and verified

params.walletId: The ID of the multi-sig wallet

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

params.description: Description of what the agent does
params.ensName: The ENS name for the agent (e.g., "kwame.agent.eth")

params.agentAddress: The smart contract address for the agent

params.canSwap: Whether agent can perform token swaps
params.endTime: Active end time (24-hour format, e.g., 1700 for 5 PM)
params.startTime: Active start time (24-hour format, e.g., 900 for 9 AM)
